"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:11:27.000Z","msg":"身邊乜人揸得啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b5600f7f0e7b584d3c62965c3ede7ad0da413ea3","tid":829712,"uid":35193,"like":11,"dislike":21,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:11:57.000Z","msg":"跟撚埋啲垃圾國家傳統<br />\n傳統中秋節都要食月餅 係咪個個人都食？<br />\n傳統新年要派利是 係咪個個都派？"},{"pid":"b9a6c295e4ada39e31274725ee84c3bc088dbc8e","tid":829712,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:11:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2910c87e5d4ae3744f63a6c3a9c45d86126ab57c","tid":829712,"uid":122287,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:12:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>身邊冇乜人揸得啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote>"},{"pid":"33c529ea08112e88722c9c96e4a2ef838f4e2ba3","tid":829712,"uid":199211,"like":7,"dislike":19,"score":-12,"quote":{"pid":"b5600f7f0e7b584d3c62965c3ede7ad0da413ea3","tid":829712,"uid":35193,"like":11,"dislike":21,"score":-10,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:11:57.000Z","msg":"跟撚埋啲垃圾國家傳統<br />\n傳統中秋節都要食月餅 係咪個個人都食？<br />\n傳統新年要派利是 係咪個個都派？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:19:10.000Z","msg":"筷子係中國傳統 你可以唔跟 用外國嘅刀叉<br />\n但你一用筷子 個人認為要跟傳統好啲<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n正如利是你大可以唔派 如果派就應該跟傳統 用翻紅色利是封<br />\n如果有人派白色利是俾你 你都覺得唔吉利/怪怪地"},{"pid":"7f64850ce485e09a0563076ade163c5d881811ff","tid":829712,"uid":15945,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:21:59.000Z","msg":"揸法啱唔啱好死既姐<br />\n你搵到比傳統方法更有效率既揸法咪吹你唔脹囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1e86cda7ed8e0bf8ba2471c8531896d83fa58c08","tid":829712,"uid":49974,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"quote":{"pid":"b9a6c295e4ada39e31274725ee84c3bc088dbc8e","tid":829712,"uid":89514,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:11:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:23:14.000Z","msg":"另一隻用虎口位+中指托住<br />\n同樓豬一樣，有次係youtubr見個外國人係用正確手勢渣筷子，嗰刻嗰得有啲冇面，連外國人都做到，點解自己係華人但做唔到，即刻用咗一兩個禮拜學<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n其實用正確手勢夾嘢係方便好多，特別係丸類、比較跣嘅食物，例如米線、軟豆腐、蒸水蛋、大件又重嘅食物等等等<br />\n交叉渣筷子係難夾以上所講嘅食物，唔想好似個傻仔咁下下用匙羹or篤住嚟食就最好學咗佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fd2345ca67b7dc9f7cfc5f8d0136cf1e9c2b5133","tid":829712,"uid":70040,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:28:49.000Z","msg":"唔一定要跟，但一定要識"},{"pid":"90b287474705a3616fa29c06d90cbb4986841e8a","tid":829712,"uid":3893,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:29:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 見到啲人揸實拳頭咁 真係好失禮"},{"pid":"6e05b5da9aa43bb7b08b51cef2580c6710fc9bf8","tid":829712,"uid":39470,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"7f64850ce485e09a0563076ade163c5d881811ff","tid":829712,"uid":15945,"like":17,"dislike":1,"score":16,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:21:59.000Z","msg":"揸法啱唔啱好死既姐<br />\n你搵到比傳統方法更有效率既揸法咪吹你唔脹囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:33:23.000Z","msg":"成日見到有人揸唔啱，夾條菜都夾極都夾唔到<br />\n仲要大大聲話夾到就得啦，使乜理佢點揸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc5167005a967a727ec94b3e71ac0b861439b0cc","tid":829712,"uid":75196,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:36:33.000Z","msg":"夾到餸就得，咩叫做岩定唔岩，一切都只係人定既標準"},{"pid":"56ccb614d48ef286154aa966eab932b70f9e9680","tid":829712,"uid":167219,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:37:51.000Z","msg":"傳統個揸法最易夾到野食<br />\n揸筆咁揸或者揸得唔好個d<br />\n一夾瓜之類難夾既野就好易夾唔到或者跌<br />\n已經唔係跟唔跟傳統既問題<br />\n係用唔用到既問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n利申：細個唔識揸筷子成日俾屋企人鬧<br />\n大個自己留意就揸返啱"},{"pid":"b2398c5facc50bbeb98d92633cc720d84283d40f","tid":829712,"uid":199211,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:45:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"050b8304f1b7fb24f23e0eabb2150a3de850763b","tid":829712,"uid":43173,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T16:57:57.000Z","msg":"其實用途上唔使跟, 但傳統揸法係經驗所得有佢好處(eg.挾圓形嘢同細笠嘢)"},{"pid":"afc9ea2837900e29d4fad15dc5e50e0dab07d313","tid":829712,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T18:35:32.000Z","msg":"洗撚咩"},{"pid":"9d5ed4ef8f76569411b42c4b49efbedc1fce8f4e","tid":829712,"uid":130177,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T19:00:45.000Z","msg":"啲人打晒交差又夾唔到嘢<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/02.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b59eb74a724e146173100a072a95f59754ed8604","tid":829712,"uid":179967,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T19:02:18.000Z","msg":"夾到咪得 好多人睇唔過眼其他人渣筷子係因為佢渣得肉酸<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5da3a4c1fc381e310ee661153e4f4cac9cb212da","tid":829712,"uid":59795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T19:16:06.000Z","msg":"細個比人笑<br />\n然後自學左半個月就揸返啱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4dcc72b6c113ac4b2daf3f2d6a5df480c86776db","tid":829712,"uid":206025,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T19:20:14.000Z","msg":"真心要 餐桌禮儀<br />\n利申 睇到人唔識揸唔會理<br />\n最緊要過到自己個關"},{"pid":"a4aec3d2e984ca529fd9d8c4c40e7c872993c5c9","tid":829712,"uid":34377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T19:22:48.000Z","msg":"唔係細個睇老豆老母，阿爺阿嫲點揸就會學識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a642734b41c4355521fa203d83901f1ace042e08","tid":829712,"uid":19305,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-09-20T19:29:50.000Z","msg":"夾到咪得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgm